review_text: Its no Parc J.J Gagnier, but it's alright I guess. Ok for kids and families although there are occasionally some unsavory characters hanging out at the picnic tables. Overall fine but if you're looking for a nice peaceful walk, I suggest you take you business to J.J Gagnier.
